    dc:description "FIGURE 21. Pedinotus glabroscutum sp. nov. (female, holotype). A, Habitus, lateral view. B, Basal segments of antenna. C, Head, front view. D, Head, dorsal view. E, Head, lateral view. F, Apex of ovipositor. G, Mesosoma, dorsal view. H, Mesosoma, lateral view. I, Propodeum and first metasomal tergite, dorsal view." ;
